| # | Finding | OWASP Category | Severity | Effort to Fix |
|---|---------|---------------|----------|--------------|
| 1 | No input validation infrastructure | A03 – Injection | 🔴 High | Low |
| 2 | No authentication on `/users` | A01 – Broken Access Control | 🔴 High | Medium |
| 3 | No security headers | A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| 4 | No rate limiting | A04 – Insecure Design | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| 5 | No CORS configuration | A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| 6 | Hardcoded port, no env config | A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Low |
| 7 | `X-Powered-By` header exposed | A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low | Low |
| 8 | No error handling middleware | A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low | Low |
| 9 | No request logging | A09 – Logging Failures | 🟡 Low | Low |

