**Line 18:** Port is hardcoded to `3000`. Configuration should come from environment variables.

```js
// Before (hardcoded)
app.listen(3000, () => { ... });

// After (configurable)
const PORT = parseInt(process.env.PORT, 10) || 3000;
app.listen(PORT, () => {
  console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`);
});
```

---

### 9. No Request Logging / Audit Trail (OWASP A09: Security Logging & Monitoring Failures)

There is zero request logging. Security incidents cannot be detected or investigated.

